---
// src/components/sections/FinalTakeaway.astro
---
<section class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[48px] p-16 text-center shadow-sm">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-10">Final Takeaway</h2>
    <div class="text-slate-400 text-lg space-y-8 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
       <p>Journaling techniques are not about filling pages. They are about building a relationship with yourself that becomes one of the most reliable resources you have.</p>
       <p>You don't need a perfect notebook, a dedicated hour, or a particularly articulate way with words. You need a willingness to be honest, a commitment to showing up regularly even when it feels pointless, and the knowledge that every page you fill is a conversation with yourself that no one else can have for you.</p>
       <p class="text-slate-800 font-bold text-xl mt-12">Pick one technique. Start tomorrow. Write three sentences. See what happens.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>